    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>侘寂（Wabi-Sabi）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入一个蘑菇弹跳的世界——这是一片充满“禅意”的空间。<br>这些带着淡淡哀愁的蘑菇，究竟想向我们诉说什么呢？<br>它们那奋力挣扎的身影，将为每位玩家带来勇气与感动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>简单操作，轻松畅玩</strong><br>直观的操作方式，无需费心思考，轻松上手。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/2713f9229d39667dc8e22063b96a3234.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/2713f9229d39667dc8e22063b96a3234.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/2713f9229d39667dc8e22063b96a3234.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>令人上瘾的触感与操作感</strong><br>顺滑细腻的动作效果，让人玩得停不下来。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/99c36de8a1356ead2e34e3939832b7b9.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/99c36de8a1356ead2e34e3939832b7b9.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/99c36de8a1356ead2e34e3939832b7b9.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>丰富的机关与皮肤</strong><br>多样化的蘑菇皮肤和独特的日式炭火烤架（七轮）自定义选项。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/961bcd15e29edc37aa4b0f518e35ce5d.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/961bcd15e29edc37aa4b0f518e35ce5d.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/961bcd15e29edc37aa4b0f518e35ce5d.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>趣味收集与探索</strong><br>收集金币解锁皮肤抽奖，还可以寻找黄金斧头进行劈柴寻宝！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/4813813906764dab00efc9510b1f3df7.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=516 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/4813813906764dab00efc9510b1f3df7.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/4813813906764dab00efc9510b1f3df7.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>感受东方神秘美学</strong><br>体验“侘寂”和“禅意”的独特世界观。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/eb88514e088e096d02580a7db37835dd.poster.avif?t=1735199216\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/eb88514e088e096d02580a7db37835dd.webm?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3300580/extras/eb88514e088e096d02580a7db37835dd.mp4?t=1735199216\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>内容分享与直播指南</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以在USAYA官方网站上查看关于视频直播和内容分享的指南。</p>",
